clir.model

Class PaperHit

  • java.lang.Object
    • clir.model.PaperHit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<PaperHit>

    public class PaperHit
extends Object
implements Comparable<PaperHit>
    A POJO to represent a paper hit (i.e. a paper returned as a recommendation given a query). It encapsulates the data that must be printed... Additionally, each element contains the number of results of the given query.
    Author:
    Gabriel
